  "prompt": "Where we can buy books online in Pune?",
  "response": "In Pune, you can buy books online from several platforms. Here are some popular options:\n\n1. **Amazon India** - A vast selection of books across various genres.\n2. **Flipkart** - Another major online retailer with a good range of books.\n3. **Bookish Santa** - An online bookstore that focuses on a wide array of titles, including indie authors.\n4. **Sapna Book House** - Offers a good collection of physical and e-books.\n5. **Books & More** - An online service that provides an extensive collection of books.\n6. **Infibeam** - An online marketplace that includes books in their inventory.\n7. **Paytm Mall** - Offers books among other products, with various discounts.\n8. **Local bookstores** - Many local independent bookstores in Pune may have an online presence or take orders online, such as Crossword and Landmark.\n\nMake sure to check for delivery options and any specific discounts or offers available on each platform.",
